Alexander Kirkland https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alexander_Kirkland 0 William Alexander Kirkland (September 15, 1901, Mexico City, Mexico – circa 1986) was a leading man in Hollywood during the early sound era, as well as a notable stage actor who starred in productions of the Group Theatre in New York.
